    <div class="AssessmentProblem.type">RestrictedConstructedResponse</div>
    <div class="AssessmentProblem.statement"><p>To make lemonade, combine 3 cups of hot water, 2 cups of sugar, and the juice from 6 lemons.&#xA0;How much of each ingredient is needed to:</p>

<ol>
	<li>triple the recipe?</li>
	<li>make half of a recipe?</li>
</ol>
</div>
    <div class="AssessmentProblem.solution"><ol>
	<li>9 cups of hot water, 6 cups of sugar, and the juice from 18 lemons.</li>
	<li>
<span class="math math-repaired" data-png-file-id="3217">\(1\frac12\)</span> cup hot water, 1 cup of sugar, and the juice from 3 lemons.</li>
</ol>
</div>
